attributes.description: Raw materials purchased. Smelted in North Carolina. Rods sent to Indiana. Re-meltd, forged and casted at headquarters. Packaging from multiple sources. Product packaged, labelled. Sent to be sterilized. Return toHeadquarters. Finished product sent to Distribution centre, Memphis. Fedex delivers product to Canada. Purulator delivers product to CBRH
